<section id="content">

<blockquote>
	<q>It took great courage to ask a beautiful young woman to marry me. Believe me, it is easier to play the whole of Petrushka on the piano.</q>
	<cite><a href="/author/140">Artur Rubinstein</a></cite>
	<footer>contributed by <a href="/contributor/38">Eric Cavanaugh</a></footer>
</blockquote>

